					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sample the background map at the four corners of the object and do bounding box on each sample that returns solid. Then you can <a href="http://pineight.com/mw/index.php?title=Four-corner_collision_detection" class="postlink">calculate wall response</a>.</div>

